<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>의사 대시보드</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/tailwind.min.css">
    <script src="/js/lucide.min.js"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-slate-50 p-6">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto space-y-6">
        <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800">의사 대시보드</h1>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-indigo-50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-indigo-600">
                        <i data-lucide="users" class="w-6 h-6"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <div class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-500">오늘 진료 환자 수</div>
                        <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800">12명</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-green-600">
                        <i data-lucide="check-circle-2" class="w-6 h-6"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <div class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-500">진료 완료</div>
                        <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800">5명</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-orange-50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-orange-600">
                        <i data-lucide="clock" class="w-6 h-6"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <div class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-500">현재 대기 중</div>
                        <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800">2명</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200 p-6">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-6">
                <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-800 flex items-center gap-2">
                    <i data-lucide="calendar" class="w-5 h-5 text-indigo-600"></i>
                    오늘의 진료 일정 미리 보기
                </h2>
                <a href="treatment-list.html" class="text-sm text-indigo-600 font-medium flex items-center gap-1 hover:text-indigo-800">
                    진료 목록 전체보기 <i data-lucide="arrow-right" class="w-4 h-4"></i>
                </a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
                <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border transition-all cursor-pointer hover:shadow-md bg-indigo-50 border-indigo-200 ring-2 ring-indigo-100" onclick="location.href='/doctor/treatment/1'">
                    <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-2">
                        <span class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-500">09:00</span>
                        <span class="text-xs font-bold px-2 py-1 rounded-lg bg-indigo-600 text-white">진료 중</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="font-bold text-slate-800 mb-1">홍길동</div>
                    <div class="text-xs text-slate-500 truncate">두통, 어지러움</div>
                </div>
                <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border transition-all cursor-pointer hover:shadow-md bg-white border-slate-200" onclick="location.href='/doctor/treatment/2'">
                    <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-2">
                        <span class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-500">09:30</span>
                        <span class="text-xs font-bold px-2 py-1 rounded-lg bg-orange-100 text-orange-600">진료 대기</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="font-bold text-slate-800 mb-1">김철수</div>
                    <div class="text-xs text-slate-500 truncate">목 통증</div>
                </div>
                <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border transition-all cursor-pointer hover:shadow-md bg-white border-slate-200" onclick="location.href='/doctor/treatment/3'">
                    <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-2">
                        <span class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-500">10:00</span>
                        <span class="text-xs font-bold px-2 py-1 rounded-lg bg-slate-100 text-slate-400">예약</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="font-bold text-slate-800 mb-1">이영희</div>
                    <div class="text-xs text-slate-500 truncate">감기 증상</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        lucide.createIcons();
    </script>
</body>
</html>
